img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13741c5a450ec89c2eceda5eca21b6f51c029ab5","tid":355201,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"乜撚野，而家公屋買番個單位都係幾十萬。<br />\n如果補地價就得，咪等於政府免息借錢俾你炒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329ae801ffd13a4eb0c16b3faecb870f3cd492a9","tid":355201,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:30:28.000Z","msg":"呢個講公平就最唔公平"},{"pid":"2f8c07a0e4b75ab93def91ea27ca5a3c697bb17f","tid":355201,"uid":634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"呢個世界本嚟就唔公平㗎啦"},{"pid":"0042d9f53efaf1a97ce5fda58d5a9ed8713d8221","tid":355201,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"私樓撚又話公屋撚打飛機<br />\n<br />\n到依家人地明買明賣又酸人唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bc68981cce5e8e49bbb82400d9dcfaa6c46445","tid":355201,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c503db7356f41d270b41b11988ffdb8e7b4154b","tid":355201,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"補地價應該加夠一億<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a4ded4526f34df9b93e5941d5e0282ad91c947","tid":355201,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>低買高賣。自由市場要補地價。 有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係賺幾十倍 <br />\n<br />\n租者置其屋計劃本身唔係想你炒賣個單位做暴發戶<br />\n而係想你下一代就算搵到/搵唔到錢都可以繼續住 令&quot;家&quot;可以傳承<br />\n<br />\n依家個個做暴發戶叫冇問題？</blockquote><br />\n如果係咁根本當初就唔應該俾人買<img src=\"/assets/